[Force Handlers]
It will run the handler task even though you have task failures.
It can also set this parameter in different areas.
* Playbook ⇒ force_handlers: true
* ansible.cfg file ⇒ force_handlers = true
* Command line argument ⇒ --force-handlers

[Ignore Errors]
It will ignore the failed task and will execute the handler tasks.
It can also set the property in Playbook.
* Playbook ⇒ ignore_errors: true
